Package: RaschR
Type: Package
Title: Pairwise Rasch Measurement Analysis and Diagnostics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Josh", "McGrane", role = c("aut", "cre"),
    email = "you@example.org")
Description: Pairwise conditional estimation of dichotomous and polytomous
    Rasch models (partial credit and rating scale), with Warm's weighted
    likelihood person estimates, the item-trait interaction chi-square,
    person separation, threshold and category diagnostics, residual
    principal-components dimensionality testing, local dependence by
    residual correlation, and differential item functioning by two-way
    residual analysis of variance. Implemented from published measurement
    theory (Choppin 1985; Andrich & Luo 1993; Warm 1989) in base R, with
    no dependence on other estimation engines.
